query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `metrics_data` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  `userId` int NOT NULL,
  `metric` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `value` text NOT NULL,
  `date` datetime NOT NULL,
  `category` varchar(100),
  `metadata` text,
  `createdAt` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
)
